beer.beer_description:
The Juice – NEIPA 
The New England IPA is storming our shores and is here to stay. 
After the success of our first attempt and more research, we are delighted with the results again!

We have used a new yeast just released in Aus called ‘Lallemand New England’ which aids in the biotransformation of hop compounds into esters - namely stone fruit and apricot. Liberal hopping during ferment with Citra, Galaxy,Nelson Sauvin and finished with Citra Lupulin powder for even more punch…get on ‘The Juice’!!
